creator: North Jersey Vineyard Church
descriptionHtml:
Come join us on the journey as we seek to know God, find freedom in our lives, discover our purpose, and make a difference in the world.

This app is packed with powerful content and resources to help you grow and stay connected with the North Jersey Vineyard wherever you are. This resource will help you easily and conveniently:
- watch services live online
- watch or listen to past messages
- stay up to date with push notifications
- access information and sign up for church events
- and more!

For more information about our church, please visit us at www.njvine.com.
descriptionShort: Powerful content and resources to help you grow and stay connected.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New in Messaging (if enabled):
- You can send files to one another
- You can mention someone using an @ symbol to notify them directly.
- Channel managers can restrict channel invites to managers
- Managers can also set artwork and descriptions for a group channel
- Administers can set channels to be public for anyone to join

Fixed:
- Media playback now stops when you force close the app
- Fixed a Messaging issue causing link previews to cause the channel to crash
